data.body:
Font changes to help with allowing bitmap fonts. 

I've tried to keep the changes as non-impacting as possible - ie - all previous configs should work - offsetY should be set to 0 by default and embedded fonts use it as such. In some cases I also had to change some checks where embedded font was checked explicitly because when only using the pixeldata there will be no embedded font.

@ilexp Please let me know what you think.
